    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "true_positive",
        "false_positive"
      ],
      "id": "s009",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "true_positive",
        "false_positive"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "为了精确描述这两种错误，我们引入四个基本计数。",
        "模型预测为正类，实际也是正类 → <term id=\"true_positive\">真正例</term>（TP）。",
        "模型预测为正类，实际是负类 → <term id=\"false_positive\">假正例</term>（FP）。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
